Subject: Fun with Floggers
Description: Come learn the ins and outs of a simple but deceptively complicated type of play: flogging. It may sound painful, it may seem simple, but when you know how, when, where, and why, you will be able to bring your partner to another plane of understanding and help them fall into the beat of the music. They will forget the rest of the world and float in another time and space. Warning: this class may lead you down a road filled with wetness, hardness, or otherwise being worshiped for your godly powers. This event is 18+.  Speakers include:Rooskie - Track: After Dark  - Duration: 1 hour
